<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>NotOnMyCard Privacy Policy</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  h2 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 32px; }
  p { margin: 8px 0; }
  .updated { color: #888; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Privacy Policy for NotOnMyCard</h1>
<p class="updated">Last Updated: February 2026</p>

<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
<p>NotOnMyCard ("we," "us," "our," or "Company") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains our data practices for our mobile application.</p>

<h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>NotOnMyCard does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. We do not collect your name, email address, location, device identifiers, or any other personal data. We do not use analytics services or track user behavior.</p>

<h2>3. How the App Works</h2>
<p>NotOnMyCard is a local multiplayer bingo game. All gameplay, card creation, and multiplayer functionality operates entirely on your device and local network. No data is sent to our servers or any third parties. We do not maintain user accounts and do not require you to provide any personal information to use the app.</p>

<h2>4. Local Network Usage</h2>
<p>The multiplayer feature uses your device's local Wi-Fi network to connect with other players on the same network. This connection is peer-to-peer and local only. No game data, player information, or network activity is transmitted outside your local network or stored by us.</p>

<h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>NotOnMyCard is designed to be family-friendly and is appropriate for all ages. Because we do not collect any personal information from any users, there is no risk of inadvertent collection of children's data. We comply fully with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA).</p>

<h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>This version of NotOnMyCard does not integrate any third-party advertising, analytics, or data collection services.</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in the app's features. We will notify you of any changes by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy. Continued use of the app after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at purenardcustoms@gmail.com.</p>

</body>
</html>
